Loops:
Loops in Java help us execute a piece of code again and again.

There are mainly 4 types of loops: for loop , while loop ,do while, loop and enhanced for loop.

Why we should learn about loop?
-because loop help us write cleaner and scalable code.
for example: if you have to test password field on a webpage you can create different variation of data 
in an excel sheet then you pick all the values one by one and test the field.

Syntax for loops:
for loop

for (starting point; condition; ending point; step size){
code that we want repeat